(5) For each left-border seed with color P[0], let track color C be the cell to its right; walk staircase (max-right through C, then max-up through C, repeat), coloring newly visited cells with cyclic P (reset per seed), and color each in-bounds blocking cell at the end of a run with M. PHASE 2: Ex1 shows palette (2,2,8) erased + staircase in 0-region with 4 caps; Ex2 shows palette (4,1) erased + staircase in 8-region with 9 caps; Ex3 shows palette (2,2,3) erased + staircase in 4-region with 8 caps → all match.
